    "en": {
      "title": "A family member was hacked to death in Balangoda",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 78-year-old man was hacked to death in Thena area of \u200b\u200bBalangoda Thotupola.",
        "Only one elderly man, E. Aberathne, a retired principal and father of six, has been murdered.",
        "The murdered person has been living alone in the house for many years. A son has come home to give food to his father this morning. The son saw the father strangled and immediately took the father to Balangoda hospital in his vehicle.",
        "The dead body has been kept at Balangoda Hospital for post-mortem examination and Ratnapura Police Crime Prevention Unit and the officials of Balangoda Police Station are conducting investigations.",
        "Also, Balangoda Court Deputy Magistrate DM Chandrasekhara came to the spot and conducted an investigation and also brought a police dog from the Ratnapura Crime Prevention Unit and conducted an investigation."
      ],
